description: Try our easy to follow Fish fingers recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Fish fingers Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 600 g cooked frozen crinkle cut chips

recipeInstructions.text: Spray well with oil spray. Cook for 15-20 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Serve with chips, lettuce and lemon wedges.
